OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin schools, report says    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Black children are disadvantaged in    
OL,6, schools because they are viewed as     
OL,7, "less innocent" and more adult-like, a 
OL,8, report says.                           
OL,10,FThe Commission on Young Lives in       
OL,11,FEngland report says this process of    
OL,12,F"adultification" means black children  
OL,13,Ffeel over-policed in schools.          
OL,15,FIt makes many feel unsafe and has a    
OL,16,Fhuge negative impact on their lives.   
OL,18,FThe government said it had strengthened
OL,19,Fsafeguarding guidance for schools, with
OL,20,Fregular training for staff.            
